sources.title: Urban Warfare | Full Movie | Steven Seagal Action | True Justice Series
sources.description:
Urban Warfare - With his background in working undercover in the war against terrorism. Kane’s history is now causing uncertainty in the team’s future when Mason and Radner are badly beaten by masked, military-trained men. Meanwhile, Sarah and Juliet are after yet another serial rapist in Seattle. The SIU team is stretched thin by the gaining strength of Seattle’s crime world.
2010.  Stars: Steven Seagal, Sarah Lind, William 'Big Sleeps' Stewart, Meghan Ory, Warren Christie
